h 8, part of the MFP newsletter. In the end, it was discussed and sent how women could increase their participation in the fight for the resumption of water sources and the lands of the former Frei Caneca plant.\n </p>\n <p>\n  Thus, the female plenary sent the formation of an agitation and advertising commission for the act to resume water sources and organize day care scale so that women can actively participate in land resumptions.\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-1 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-171339\" data-id=\"171339\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" height=\"480\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/640x480_IMG-20240317-WA0046.limpo_.jpg\" srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/640x480_IMG-20240317-WA0046.limpo_.jpg\" width=\"640\"/>\n   <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">\n    Mesa had a popular school teacher, representative of LCP-Ne and CDRA representative. Photo: Database and\n   </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-171338\" data-id=\"171338\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"480\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/640x480_IMG-20240317-WA0045.limpo_.jpg\" srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/640x480_IMG-20240317-WA0045.limpo_.jpg\" width=\"640\"/>\n   <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">\n    Assembly was preceded by intense mobilization. Photo: Database and\n   </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-171337\" data-id=\"171337\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"480\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" src=\"https://anovademocrac